r"""
MAIL CHAINS -> ONE SUMMARY (DOCX + HTML + PDF) — Single-cell, notebook-friendly
=============================================================================

What it does
- Scans .msg files (recursively) in MAIL_DIRS
- Extracts conversation text (tries to put the OLDEST message first)
- Optionally ingests loose PDFs and loose images if found in same folders
- Summarizes with AzureOpenAI (GenAI-Nexus) using a map-reduce pattern
- Outputs: DOCX + HTML + (optional) PDF + a stats JSON + failures log

Hardening
- Fixes regex compile error (no inline (?i) flags in joined patterns)
- Sanitizes text to reduce Azure "jailbreak" prompt filter triggers
- Retries smaller chunk if model returns empty
"""

